metadata.name: BUNNICORN #1
metadata.description: Bunnicorns is a community-driven 500 supply NFT project that aims to bring together a unique collection of adorable creatures with their own stories; while providing incentives and rewards for its holders through daily ETH giveaways, staking rewards, and partnerships with blue-chip projects. The ultimate objective is to develop a thriving community where Bunnicorns holders can flourish.
